ton\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ird1665702714456.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ird1665702714456.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ird1665702714456.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ird1665702714456\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Signature\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ird1665702714456__signature_317911\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Signature is a Development Object that describes the remote interface of a\n      component, or modeled entity operation. Signatures for Uniface components and modeled entity\n      operations are automatically generated, but signatures for non-Uniface components that Uniface\n      can call at runtime, must be explicitly defined.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ird1665702714456__topic_d64747e1_d64748e1_d64749e1_d64750e1_d64751e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d256785e53\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sig</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qnm1665702714020.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnm1665702714020.html\" title=\"A Signature Implementation is a Development Object that defines the technology used to implement a signature, such as Uniface, COM, SOAP and so on. A Signature can have multiple implementations. Each Signature Implementation captures the technology-specific properties of the Signature, Signature Operation, and Signature Parameters.\">Signature Implementation</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dlk1665702714091.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlk1665702714091.html\" title=\"A Signature Operation is a Development Object that describes the public method of a signature.\">Signature Operation</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"srw1665702550375.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/srw1665702550375.html\" title=\"A Main Development Object is a Development Object that has no parent object, is maintained using a dedicated editor, and can be saved and exported as a single unit, with all its children.\">Main Development Object</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Component Signature, Entity Collection Signature, Occurrence Collection Signature</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>.sig</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Depending on the implementations, it may generate the following files: <span class=\"ph filepath\">.wsdl</span>, <span class=\"ph filepath\">.cfg</span>, <span class=\"ph filepath\">.dll</span>, <span class=\"ph filepath\">.fml</span>, Java stub, C stub</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ird1665702714456__table_d10781e1_d10782e1_d10783e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">sig:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">sig:<var class=\"keyword varname\">EntityName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613770\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613770\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Signature Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Signature A Signature is a Development Object that describes the remote interface of a component, or modeled entity operation. Signatures for Uniface components and modeled entity operations are automatically generated, but signatures for non-Uniface components that Uniface can call at runtime, must be explicitly defined. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: sig Main Development Object? No. Part of: — Contains: Signature Implementation , Signature Operation , Property Generalization: Main Development Object Specializations: Component Signature, Entity Collection Signature, Occurrence Collection Signature Compilation output: ComponentName .sig Depending on the implementations, it may generate the following files: .wsdl , .cfg , .dll , .fml , Java stub, C stub URI format: sig: ComponentName sig: EntityName Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}